## Dataset

This project uses the IMDB Movie Reviews Dataset. The dataset can be found on Kaggle:

[https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/harshitshankhdhar/imdb-dataset-of-top-1000-movies-and-tv-shows](kaggle)

**Instructions to use the dataset:**

1.  Download the `IMDB Dataset.csv` file from the Kaggle link above.
2.  Place the downloaded `IMDB Dataset.csv` file into a folder named `data/` in the root directory of this project. (Or, if your code expects it in the root, just say "Place it in the root directory").
3.  Alternatively, you can use the Kaggle API to download the dataset directly. See instructions below.
4.  or directly upload code and the dataset in google colab and the code will run successfully.
